.DT
register_special_attack
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
register_special_attack

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
register_special_attack -  This method adds a special attack callback into our special attack queue.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void register_special_attack(int type,
int flags,
string ob,
string fun,
mixed data,
int expire)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of the special attack
%^BOLD%^flags%^RESET%^ - the stage flags for the special attack
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the name of the callback object
%^BOLD%^fun%^RESET%^ - the name of the callback function
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - any data specific to the special attack
%^BOLD%^expire%^RESET%^ - the time after which this special should expire

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/combat.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a special attack callback into our special attack queue.
.EP

